<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        nav {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        nav a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #333;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 0 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
        }

        section {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>Welcome to the Home Page</h1>
    </header>

    <nav>
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/about">About</a>
        <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>

    <section>
        <h2>Introduction</h2>
        <p>This is a simple home page designed for demonstration purposes. You can add more content and features as needed.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Features</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Easy navigation</li>
            <li>Responsive design</li>
            <li>Clean and minimalistic</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Your Website. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
